{"about_the_game":"<u><strong>Murder at the Birch Tree Theater</strong>: A Musical Theater Murder Mystery</u><br><br>Uncover high drama in this whodunnit set in a small-town community theater!  Gather clues by investigating the sets, casts and backstage crews of 10 theatrical productions, using their stories to piece together each deadly crime.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864590/extras/Cassidy_blink.gif?t=1736363524\" /><br><br><strong>Explore the theater for clues</strong><br>The game features 10 levels -- each focused on a deadly incident that occurs during a performance.<br><br><strong>Solve mysteries</strong><br>Gather clues and observe each scenario to deduce what happened. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864590/extras/Shelia_anim.gif?t=1736363524\" /><br><br><strong>Piece it together</strong><br>Infer the story from clues and environments, then fill in the blanks to progress.<br><br><strong>Take a backstage tour</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Every level features a theatrical production that is incorporated into the puzzles and environment.<br></li><li>The soundtrack draws inspiration from Broadway musicals of the 20th century.<br></li><li>The all-animal cast has been lovingly hand-drawn, and is full of rich backstories, dilemmas, and desires.  <br></li><li>A larger narrative is inferred through clues and environmental storytelling.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864590/extras/Chaz_anim.gif?t=1736363524\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864590/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736363524","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2864590/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736363524","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/